CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 13, 1957, pg. A8, reads: "Party Conversation - These young people didn't spend the entire evening conversing, but followed the usual party procedure of dancing and devouring the food. The party was held at the residence of Timmy Williams, and was hosted by Timmy. Wynn Jones, Charles (Hambone) Hampton, Ronnie Talbert, Stan Waters, Nikki Nickens, Bob Worthington, Butch Thomas and Alan James. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Young women and men gathered in living room for party in home of Timmy Williams
